[I] A simple music player aiming to provide a nice experience for its users

[T] With Elisa, you can browse your local music collection by genre, artist,
[T] album, or track, listen to online radio, create and manage playlists,
[T] display lyrics, and more.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/elisa/

